snippet.title: Orrin Luc
snippet.description:
I make video essays that celebrate cinema's influence on video games.  Sometimes, I explore the limitations of adapting cinema form to games.  

Follow me on Letterboxd at https://letterboxd.com/oluc/ if you would like to read my movie reviews.

Check out my Let's Play channel, itsluckfam, if you desire to watch my quixotic attempt at comedy: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCCNEJa9iwF4l32p4EVmfs6A

Also, I podcast with the fine folks at Jump Crouch where we talk games and pop culture: https://open.spotify.com/show/0CVmW8s6FdkPF56C1Ccb0i?si=rtoS8FseT9KASX6LFgKvNw&dl_branch=1&nd=1

My Twitter Account: twitter.com/BadFilmTakes1
